items.title: 'Haves and have-nots': The stock market thinks more consumers are reaching a breaking point
items.description: Wall Street is growing wary of the consumer as disappointing earnings, weak sector flows, and tariff pressures expose cracks in household demand, particularly among lower-income Americans.
